<i>noun</i>: 聖靈, 성령 <br>
<ul>
<li>
<i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>聖靈, 성령</dt><br>
<dd>the third person in the Trinity; Jesus promised the Apostles that he would send the Holy Spirit after his Crucifixion and Resurrection; it came on Pentecost</dd><br>
<dd><i>synonyms</i>: Holy Spirit, Holy Ghost, Paraclete, Perfecter of the Elect, Comforter, God the Holy Spirit</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>
